'''''Perspectives in Vascular Surgery and Endovascular Therapy''''' is a quarterly [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[medical journal]] that covers research in the field of [[angiology]]. Its [[editor-in-chief]] is Peter Gloviczki ([[Mayo Medical School]]). It was established in 1988 and is currently published by [[Sage Publications]].

== Abstracting and indexing ==
''Perspectives in Vascular Surgery and Endovascular Therapy'' is abstracted and indexed in [[CINAHL]] and [[MEDLINE]].

